cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper focuses on face super-resolution using a convolutional neural network, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of attention maps and segmentation networks also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of upsampling techniques and image quality enhancement could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
